* Badger, Anthony. ''FDR: The First Hundred Days'' (2008) 200pp; overview by leading British scholar ISBN 0-8090-4441-2
* {{Cite book |ref=Ball |last=Ball |first=Howard |title=Hugo L. Black: Cold Steel Warrior |publisher= Oxford University Press |year=2006 |isbn=0-19-507814-4}}
